data.description: North Longview Gem! Welcome to your new home in the cul-de-sac! This charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath residence offers spacious living, boasting an impressive 2062 square feet of living space, situated on a generous 0.6940-acre lot.  As you approach the property, you are greeted by a beautifully landscaped front yard and a welcoming porch, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or watching the sunset. Step inside and be captivated by the warm and inviting atmosphere that flows throughout the home. Cozy up by the fireplace on cooler evenings and relax with family and friends.  Retreat upstairs to the spacious master suite, complete with a private ensuite bathroom. Two additional bedrooms downstairs provide ample space for family members or guests and share a full bathroom.  Step outside and discover your own personal oasis. The expansive backyard offers endless possibilities, whether you envision creating a private garden, installing a pool, or simply enjoying outdoor activities. The large porch is perfect for summer barbecues and outdoor game nights.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this North Longview gem your forever home. Schedule your private tour today and experience the charm and tranquility this property has to offer!  -Seller is offering a $5,000 flooring allowance
